This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with the use of machine learning technology to detect clickbait messages. Additionally, the paper may also belong to cs.IR (Information Retrieval) as clickbait detection involves analyzing and retrieving information from social media. The use of machine learning algorithms also suggests that the paper may belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, since clickbait detection involves identifying and preventing malicious content, the paper may also belong to cs.CR (Cryptography and Security).
